SUMMARY:Hyper-Local Happy Hour (Non-alcoholic)
DTSTAMP:20260314T154855Z
DTSTART:20260324T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get to know your hyper-local Capitol Hill neighbors around Cal 
	Anderson Park in an open house style\, non-alcoholic happy hour!  Enjoy no
	n-alcoholic beers and yummy mocktails\, along with a charcuterie spread\, 
	all inside a 120-year-old historic Capitol Hill church building. These hap
	py hours will be from 4-5:30pm every 4th Tuesday through June \n\nJanuary 
	27th\n\nFebruary 24th\n\nMarch 24th\n\nApril 28th\n\nMay 26th\n\nJune 23rd
	\n\n\\*Please note that ADA access is available into the happy hour area\,
	 but not to the restrooms unfortunately \\(very old building!\\)\n\nhttps:
	//seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/hyper-local-happy-hour-non-alcohol
	ic/17896454/2026-03-24T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
